   <taskbody>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Connect the signal cables from the temperature sensor to
the control terminal block X011 terminals 1 (red wire), 2 (brown wire),
3 (black wire), and 4 (yellow wire) in the main battery cabinet.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Route the signal cables from the control terminal block
X011 terminals 1–4 through the bottom of the main battery cabinet
and connect to the external connection board J1603 terminals 1–4
in the UPS cabinet. (This cable is not supplied).</cmd>
